      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        rf-dcc-dpz-cli       =    spaces
                     go to prn-sel-rec-800.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Bufferizzazione codice cliente              *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      rf-dcc-cod-cli       to   w-sel-rec-dcc-cli      .
